description: This source file is a React-like component written in TSX for a Qwik-based front-end application. It defines an 'EditNotePage' component that allows editing a note identified by its 'id' parameter, rendering a 'NoteEditor' component with initial values and save/cancel logic. It also exports a page head configuration for setting the page title and meta description.

methods.name: Component
methods.description: Main component function for editing a note, utilizing Qwik's component$.
